  "title": "Architectural Coordinator Cum Drafter",
  "description": "<h4>Job Description</h4>\n<p><strong>JOB SCOPE</strong></p>\n<p>Responsible for executing the company projects in architectural works in building construction which covers:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Review project specifications, technical clarifications and construction drawings</li>\n  <li>Carry out works scheduling, material requisition, cost control, project supervision and documentation</li>\n  <li>Supervise architectural works and coordinate with client’s representatives, consultants and sub-contractors on technical matters</li>\n  <li>Supervise to achieve quality of works and to comply with safety &amp; environmental regulations</li>\n  <li>Supervise project activities to comply with the Company’s ISO system</li>\n  <li>Study all the drawing and prepare for shop drawing submission and get approval from consultants</li>\n  <li>To prepare all the As-Built drawing in the final stage</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>JOB REQUIREMENTS</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Diploma / Degree in Architectural </li>\n  <li>Minimum 2 years relevant experience in supervision of architectural works in building/warehouse/HDB/maintenance construction</li>\n  <li>Minimum 2 years relevant experience in drafting using the software</li>\n  <li>Good communicative skills, able to interact with people of all levels and teamwork</li>\n  <li>Prefer PR / Singapore Citizen</li>\n</ul>",
  "minimumYearsExperience": 2,
